transcript:
Customer: Kuch toh log kahenge logon ka kaam hai kehna.
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan haan sir aawaz kaise aa rahi hai ab?
Executive: Haan bataiye kya keh rahe hain?
Customer: Haan sir yeh bolna tha jaise ki maine baat kiya tha sir se toh woh bol rahe the ki humko pehle se ab kaafi achche matlab bylist mein kaafi achcha lead aa rahi hai sir aapko balki bhi aapki lead aa rahi hai na sir?
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Toh abhi aap.
Executive: Haan sab baat theek hai aapki aa rahi hai aa rahi hai aapne toh jo pehle contract hai us contract ko toh pura karo pehle.
Customer: Haan sir uska maine bol diya aaj aapko sir 20 non-lapsable bylist aapko provide karwate hain sir theek hai aaj aaj maine baat kar liya aapko kya aapne do teen mahine pehle baat hui thi ki aaj ho jayegi 24 ghante mein ho jayegi apan uske baad maine kuch bola hi nahi toh aap logon ki taraf se toh koi response hi nahi hai.
Executive: Haan haan sir maine unse baat haan haan sir maine actually main sorry bolta hu sir aapko aaj main aapko provide karwata hu theek hai sir non-lapsable bylist aur abhi jaise main dekh raha hu sir abhi aap koi issue aa raha hai sir aise bylist mein convert ho rahi hai bylist aapki jo bhi aa rahi hai sir.
Customer: Deal.
Executive: Haan ho rahi hai woh toh chal rahi hai abhi aaj toh abhi mere leaden khatam ho gayi abhi toh.
Customer: Haan abhi main dekh raha hu abhi aapke paas balance mein abhi aapke paas ek bylist hai sir aapke paas hai na daily wali.
Executive: Woh daily bonus wali woh toh ab wapas Sunday ko milegi nahi toh.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai main aaj sir se meri baat ho gayi aaj aapko non-lapsable bylist dilwate hain theek hai sir.
Customer: Theek hai toh yeh yeh kaam tha aur aur kya kaam bataya tha bhaiya ne aapko isme kya karna tha mere profile pe.
Executive: Aur toh aapko woh social media ka bataya tha sir hai na sir.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Haan toh social media pe sir aapko page banane padenge uske baad jo aapko isme jaise product hote hain na hamare product product hote hain sir usme fir aapko video attach kar deni hai niche option aata hai add video ka sir isme aap apni aapke isme app pe milega ya mere ko kya karna hai mere social media pe mere ko page alag se banana hai yu.
Executive: Haan sir aapko page aise banane ke baad isme option aata hai aapke product niche aap dekhenge add add video ka sir hai na sir toh udhar pe aap apni video attach kar sakte hain isse aapka promotion hota rahega sir aapka isme dekhiye jaise aap dekhiye isme option aa raha hai sir abhi aap jaise open karenge na product isme add video mein toh udhar option aata hai instagram youtube waise aap direct link kar sakte hain sir apna social media account sir.
Customer: Idhar se yeh aapko waha pe waha pe waha pe add kar sakte hain theek hai.
Executive: Haan yeh dekhiye abhi jaise aap abhi kariye kya sir video meet ke liye abhi.
Customer: Kyu sir?
Executive: Haan woh na.
Executive: Haan toh abhi main link share karta hu aapko dikha dunga sir kaise kya karte hain theek hai sir karo fir.
Customer: Abhi aapke aa sakte hain link.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai kya kya karta hu theek hai.
Customer: Haan sir.
